                "invention-title": [
                    "Steel mill secondary energy recycling and hydrogen metallurgy method and system and application of steel mill secondary energy recycling and hydrogen metallurgy method and system",
                    "一种钢厂二次能源回收利用与氢冶金方法、系统及其应用"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a steel mill secondary energy recycling and hydrogen metallurgy method and system and application of the steel mill secondary energy recycling and hydrogen metallurgy method and system. The method comprises the following steps: obtaining by-product coal gas of a steel mill, separating out reducing gas, and introducing the reducing gas into a hydrogen-based shaft furnace to produce sponge iron; the reducing gas comprises first decarburized gas, second decarburized gas, third decarburized and denitrified gas and hydrogen, or comprises the first decarburized gas, the third decarburized and denitrified gas and hydrogen; the first decarburized gas is obtained by decarburizing FINEX gas, the second decarburized gas is obtained by decarburizing converter gas, the third decarburized and denitrified gas is obtained by decarburizing and denitrifying hydrogen-based shaft furnace top gas, and the hydrogen is obtained by extracting hydrogen from coke oven gas; and extracting hydrogen from the coke oven gas to obtain fourth desorbed gas, and blowing the fourth desorbed gas into the blast furnace for low-carbon smelting production of liquid molten iron. The method has important significance in utilizing secondary energy of a steel mill, reducing primary energy consumption of the hydrogen-based shaft furnace and reducing carbon emission of the blast furnace."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种钢厂二次能源回收利用与氢冶金方法、系统及其应用。所述方法包括：获取钢厂副产煤气，分离出还原性气体，通入氢基竖炉生产海绵铁；还原性气体包括第一脱碳气、第二脱碳气、第三脱碳脱氮气和氢气，或，包括第一脱碳气、第三脱碳脱氮气和氢气；第一脱碳气由FINEX煤气脱碳而得，第二脱碳气由转炉煤气脱碳而得，第三脱碳脱氮气由氢基竖炉顶煤气脱碳脱氮而得，氢气由焦炉煤气经提氢而得；焦炉煤气经提氢还得第四解吸气，第四解吸气喷吹入高炉用于低碳冶炼生产液态铁水。本发明对于利用钢厂二次能源，降低氢基竖炉一次能源消耗，降低高炉碳排放具有重要意义。"
                }
